/4e086/IMG_20170404_112101-scaled-1.jpg 1301w,\n/static/7b086339cb1f17e93f7be33fccb6bfd7/0029e/IMG_20170404_112101-scaled-1.jpg 1734w,\n/static/7b086339cb1f17e93f7be33fccb6bfd7/bb9a8/IMG_20170404_112101-scaled-1.jpg 2560w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 867px) 100vw, 867px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 867px) 100vw, 867px\" srcset=\"/static/7b086339cb1f17e93f7be33fccb6bfd7/756f1/IMG_20170404_112101-scaled-1.jpg 217w,\n/static/7b086339cb1f17e93f7be33fccb6bfd7/3e5a1/IMG_20170404_112101-scaled-1.jpg 434w,\n/static/7b086339cb1f17e93f7be33fccb6bfd7/7bd22/IMG_20170404_112101-scaled-1.jpg 867w,\n/static/7b086339cb1f17e93f7be33fccb6bfd7/4e086/IMG_20170404_112101-scaled-1.jpg 1301w,\n/static/7b086339cb1f17e93f7be33fccb6bfd7/0029e/IMG_20170404_112101-scaled-1.jpg 1734w,\n/static/7b086339cb1f17e93f7be33fccb6bfd7/bb9a8/IMG_20170404_112101-scaled-1.jpg 2560w\" src=\"/static/7b086339cb1f17e93f7be33fccb6bfd7/7bd22/IMG_20170404_112101-scaled-1.jpg\" alt=\"Kings &amp; Queens of Good Hearts Fun-Raiser Check Presentation\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nThis year’s Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Gala was such a success as we raised over $350,000 for charities in San Antonio and the surrounding areas. Yesterday, those charities received their checks at a press conference held by The PM Group to recognize the wonderful work these non-profit organizations do in our community.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nWe can’t say thank you enough to all who attended and donated to our worthy charities. All funds raised benefit ChildSafe, SA YES, C.A.R.E., Children In Need, San Antonio Sports, Mission: Miracle K9 Rescue, San Antonio Pets Alive, UTSA Roadrunner Athletic Fund, 100 Club of San Antonio, Triumph Over Kid Cancer and God&#8217;s Dogs Rescue. These organizations do such important work in our community, and we are so glad we can support them in their journey. With over 1,000 people who attended, we know we have made such a positive impact to the charities who benefit from the money raised.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<div itemprop=\"video\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\">\n<h2><span itemprop=\"name\">2017 Kings &#038; Queens of Good Hearts Fun-Raiser</span></h2>\n<p><meta itemprop=\"duration\" content=\"PT1M45S\" /><meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2017-02-16T16:59:19Z\"/><meta itemprop=\"thumbnailURL\" content=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/oDEpdASH700/hqdefault.jpg\" /><meta itemprop=\"interactionCount\" content=\"35\" /><meta itemprop=\"embedURL\" content=\"https://youtube.googleapis.com/v/oDEpdASH700\" /></p>\n<div id=\"schema-videoobject\" class=\"video-container\"><iframe width=\"853\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/oDEpdASH700?rel=0&#038;controls=0&#038;showinfo=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><span itemprop=\"description\">The PM Group&#8217;s annual Fun-Raiser Gala for San Antonio charities.</span>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n<strong>About The PM Group:</strong> The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 29 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <em>San Antonio Business Journal</em>. The PM Group’s client roster spans various industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala that to date raised over $1 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations.</p>\n","title":"Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Gala Raises Over $350K for Local Charities","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Gala Raises Over $350K for Local Charities","url":"/kings-and-queens-of-good-hearts-gala-raises-over-350k-for-local-charities/"}],"title":"Kings & Queens Gala Raises $350K for Charities | The PM Group","metaDesc":"This year's Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Gala raised over $350,000 for charities in San Antonio and surrounding areas.","focuskw":"Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Gala","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"Kings & Queens Gala Raises $350K for Charities | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"This year's Kings and Queens of Good Hearts Gala raised over $350,000 for charities in San Antonio and surrounding areas.","opengraphImage":{"altText":"Kings & Queens of Good Hearts Fun-Raiser Check Presentation","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/kings-queens-nw-1.jpg","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/kings-queens-nw-1-300x224.jpg 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/kings-queens-nw-1-768x574.jpg 768w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/kings-queens-nw-1.jpg 800w"},"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/kings-and-queens-of-good-hearts-gala-raises-over-350k-for-local-charities/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/#website\",\"url\":\"/\",\"name\":\"The PM Group\",\"description\":\"San Antonio\\u2019s Largest Advertising and Marketing Agency\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"target\":{\"@type\":\"EntryPoint\",\"urlTemplate\":\"/?s={search_term_string}\"},\"query-input\":\"required name=search_term_string\"}],\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\"},{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"@id\":\"/kings-and-queens-of-good-hearts-gala-raises-over-350k-for-local-charities/#primaryimage\",\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"url\":\"/static/43f964568a35a91f461ce6a1b576e148/kings-queens-nw-1.jpg\",\"contentUrl\":\"/static/43f964568a35a91f461ce6a1b576e148/kings-queens-nw-1.jpg\",\"width\":800,\"height\":598,\"caption\":\"Kings & Queens of Good Hearts Fun-Raiser Check Presentation\"},{\"@type\":\"We